rena]], [[Tallinn]], Estonia\n|{{fb|Estonia}}\n|<center>0\u2013'''1'''</center>\n|<center>0\u20132<ref>According to the [http://en.archive.uefa.com/competitions/euro2012/history/season=2008/round=2241/match=83930/index.html UEFA report] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160114103457/http://en.archive.uefa.com/competitions/euro2012/history/season%3D2008/round%3D2241/match%3D83930/index.html |date=14 January 2016 }}, this goal was scored by player V. Bystrov.  In Russia, the UEFA report has no legal force, and is not recognized, and the goal is credited to player A. Kerzhakov. He scored 2 goals.</ref></center>\n|[[UEFA Euro 2008 qualification]]\n|-\n|9\n|2007-03-24\n|[[A. Le Coq Arena]], [[Tallinn]], Estonia\n|{{fb|Estonia}}\n|<center>0\u2013'''2'''</center>\n|<center>0\u20132</center>\n|[[UEFA Euro 2008 qualification]]\n|-\n|10\n|2007-06-02\n|[[Petrovsky Stadium]], [[Saint Petersburg]], Russia\n|{{fb|Andorra}}\n|<center>'''1'''\u20130</center>\n|<center>4\u20130</center>\n|[[UEFA Euro 2008 qualification]]\n|-\n|11\n|2007-06-02\n|[[Petrovsky Stadium]], [[Saint Petersburg]], Russia\n|{{fb|Andorra}}\n|<center>'''2'''\u20130</center>\n|<center>4\u20130</center>\n|[[UEFA Euro 2008 qualification]]\n|-\n|12\n|2007-06-02\n|[[Petrovsky Stadium]], [[Saint Petersburg]], Russia\n|{{fb|Andorra}}\n|<center>'''3'''\u20130</center>\n|<center>4\u20130</center>\n|[[UEFA Euro 2008 qualification]]\n|-\n|13\n|2007-09-08\n|[[Lokomotiv Stadium (Moscow)|Lokomotiv Stadium]], Moscow, Russia\n|{{fb|Macedonia}}\n|<center>'''3'''\u20130</center>\n|<center>3\u20130</center>\n|[[UEFA Euro 2008 qualification]]\n|-\n|14\n|2009-06-10\n|[[Helsinki Olympic Stadium]], Helsinki, Finland\n|{{fb|Finland}}\n|<center>0\u2013'''1'''</center>\n|<center>0\u20133</center>\n|[[2010 FIFA World Cup qualification]]\n|-\n|15\n|2009-06-10\n|[[Helsinki Olympic Stadium]], Helsinki, Finland\n|{{fb|Finland}}\n|<center>0\u2013'''2'''</center>\n|<center>0\u20133</center>\n|[[2010 FIFA World Cup qualification]]\