jona Formation]] || {{flag|Spain}} || [[Europe]]\n|-\n| [[Calcarenites of Sant Elm]] || {{flag|Spain}} || [[Europe]]\n|-\n| || {{flag|Turkey}} || [[Europe]]\n|-\n| [[Monterey Formation]] || {{USA}} || [[North America]]\n|-\n| [[Puente Formation]] || {{USA}} || [[North America]]\n|-\n| [[Purisima Formation]] || {{USA}} || [[North America]]\n|-\n| [[San Mateo Formation]] || {{USA}} || [[North America]]\n|-\n| [[Santa Margarita Formation]] || {{USA}} || [[North America]]\n|-\n| [[Temblor Formation]] || {{USA}} || [[North America]]\n|-\n| [[Topanga Formation]] || {{USA}} || [[North America]]\n|-\n| [[Bone Valley Formation]] || {{USA}} || [[North America]]\n|-\n| [[Calvert Formation]] || {{USA}} || [[North America]]\n|-\n| [[Kirkwood Formation, United States|Kirkwood Formation]] || {{USA}} || [[North America]]\n|-\n| || {{flag|Barbados}} || [[North America]]\n|-\n| [[Coj\u00edmar Formation]] || {{flag|Cuba}} || [[North America]]\n|-\n| [[Kendance Formation]] || {{flag|Grenada}} || [[North America]]\n|-\n| || {{flag|Jamaica}} || [[North America]]\n|-\n| [[Aymam\u00f3n Limestone]] || {{flag|Puerto Rico}} || [[North America]]\n|-\n| [[Almejas Formation]] || {{flag|Mexico}} || [[North America]]\n|-\n| [[Carrillo Puerto Formation]] || {{flag|Mexico}} || [[North America]]\n|-\n| [[Chagres Formation]] || {{flag|Panama}} || [[North America]]\n|-\n| [[Chucunaque Formation]] || {{flag|Panama}} || [[North America]]\n|-\n| [[Gat\u00fan Formation]] || {{flag|Panama}} || [[North America]]\n|-\n| [[Paran\u00e1 Formation]] || {{flag|Argentina}} || [[South America]]\n|-\n| [[Bah\u00eda Inglesa Formation]] || {{flag|Chile}} || [[South America]]\n|-\n| [[Castilletes Formation]] || {{flag|Colombia}} || [[South America]]\n|-\n| [[Miramar Formation, Peru|Miramar Formation]] || {{flag|Peru}} || [[South America]]\n|-\n| [[Pisco Formation]] || {{flag|Peru}} || [[South America]]\n|-\n| [[Camacho Formation]] || {{flag|Uruguay}} || [[South America]]\n|-\n| [[Cantaure Formation, Venezuela|Cantaure F