of legendary creatures, [[Land Beneath the Ground!|the Terra-firmians]], only to end up trapped underground with Mrs. Beakley, Louie, Dewey, and Launchpad. As they struggle to escape, Launchpad becomes more and more paranoid, leaving Dewey to help him come back to his senses. Huey and Webby meanwhile argue over the creatures' existence, as the former believes only in his [[Junior Woodchucks|Junior Woodchuck]] Guidebook and is afraid to do anything that doesn't follow its instructions. In the end however, the two reconcile and find out that the Terra-firmians are actually real. In the midst of their adventure, Lena struggles to gain Mrs. Beakley's trust while secretly receiving instructions from Magica ([[Catherine Tate]]).\n|LineColor        = FFEF00\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 6\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 6\n |Title           = The House of the Lucky Gander!\n |DirectedBy      = Matthew Humphreys & Tom Owens\n |WrittenBy       = {{StoryTeleplay|s=Francisco Angones, Madison Bateman, Colleen Evanson, Christian Magalhaes & Bob Snow|t=Magalhaes}}\n |Aux2            = Dalton E. Grant Jr., Vaughn Tada & Brandon Warren\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|10|14}}{{efn|name=oct14|On [[Disney XD (Canada)|Disney XD Canada]], the episodes \"The Infernal Internship of Mark Beaks!\" and \"The House of the Lucky Gander!\" aired in an inverted order, on October 14, 2017<ref>{{cite web|title=DISNEY XD CANADA October 14th listing|url=https://www.tvpassport.com/tv-listings/stations/disney-xd-canada/17172|website=TV Passport|publisher=TV Media Inc.|accessdate=16 October 2017|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20171014132743/https://www.tvpassport.com/tv-listings/stations/disney-xd-canada/17172|archivedate=October 14, 2017|date=14 October 2017|url-status=dead|df=mdy-all}}</ref> and October 21, 2017<ref>{{cite web|title=DISNEY XD CANADA October 21st listing|url=https://www.tvpassport.com/tv-listings/stations/disney-xd-canada/17172|website=TV Passport|publisher=TV Media Inc.|acce